text: Damn solid tze char. God tier wok hey that is so intense you might cry your eyes out from pure joy. He cooks with the passion of the God of Cookery 食神 himself. To this maestro of the wok, cooking isn’t just a profession, it’s his life, and you can taste that devotion in every bite.
Tasty food with generous portions. Chef has been in the neighbourhood for past 10 years. Big sitting area and airy.

Ordered a salted fish fried rice and was extremely happy with the choice. This is a dish that most "ze char" stall provides but I would rank it top on my list among all those I have tasted. The rice full of "wok hei", the salted fish crispy and frequent.
Superb tasty food & hotpot!!! The LaLa Hotpot soup us Super Power!!! Prawns, LaLa & prawn paste super fresh!!! Mutton meat also super fresh!!!  Highly recommended!!!👍👍👍🥰🥰🥰

A very simple salted fish fried rice and kailan vegetable, but they are so delicious 😋😋
Really good 👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼
